{"tid":763673,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE、BLACKPINK、MAMAMOO都做不到的事情，ZICO和IU做到了！","createTime":"2018-08-01T10:19:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T02:02:25.000Z","uid":34643,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2ceb9c5bb45d9a7934ce8b4dfb667cfa000908be","tid":763673,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T10:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2018-07-31/107936-640035.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2018-07-31%2F107936-640035.jpg&h=db28b9a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網友：不愧是音源強者，直接打敗機器！<br />\n<br />\nZICO X IU的新歌《SoulMate》於30日18點公開，並根據iChat的資料顯示，該首歌於31日中午登上榜頂，席捲7大音樂網站1位，All-Kill！<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2018-07-31/107936-640040.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2018-07-31%2F107936-640040.png&h=8a34d211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2018-07-31/107936-640041.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2018-07-31%2F107936-640041.png&h=469ed28f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尤為引起話題的原因是，ZICO X IU阻斷了有刷榜嫌疑的Shaun連續兩個星期的強勢。 各大人氣女團的新歌都沒能做到的事情，ZICO和IU做到了。 網友感歎：「ZICO和IU不愧是最強組合」、「不是打敗Shaun，是打敗演算法了」、「IU是塗了蜂蜜嗎，怎麼那麼甜」等等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2018-07-31/107936-640039.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2018-07-31%2F107936-640039.jpg&h=8c87aced&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Vl1kO9hObpA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVl1kO9hObpA&d=g3iezlzfjZCFaFCYhwwWlrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=27746e94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Vl1kO9hObpA</a>"},{"pid":"e94a26c59f96aabb874a4208aa4842484ee86dbc","tid":763673,"uid":34643,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T10:24:09.000Z","msg":"網友評論<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/